title: PES6 Option File Actualizado/Updated 2013
description:
This is just an option file I edited myself using PES Editor 6.

I used Soccer Wiki (http://soccerwiki.org/wiki.php) as database. This is the most accurate source I know about.

The Option File update is not complete, however, some young players from major teams are created.

The Faces of New Players need to be edited.

The Emblems of the newly promoted teams need to be edited as well.

The recently Retired Players are still in the game as Free Players.

Last transfer season: September 2013.


- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Works with Pro Evolution Soccer 6 (PES6), PC version.

File size: 1,91 k

Originally uploaded by me.

Feel free to keep on editing, sharing, destroying, copying, pasting and whatever you want to do without letting me or anyone know.
